---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Life Reflections">
  <h2 style="color: #003366;">Reflections & Milestones</h2>
  
  <article style="background: white; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 15px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <div style="height: 250px; background: #eef2f7; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #a2c2e1;">
      <span>[Photo of your new home or graduation]</span>
    </div>
    
    <div style="padding: 25px;">
      <span style="background: #e1f0ff; color: #0056b3; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: bold;">Gratitude</span>
      <h3 style="margin: 15px 0 10px 0;">A Season of Blessings</h3>
      <p style="color: #444; line-height: 1.8;">
        I am so grateful for the blessings I have been given in this lifetime. 
        Both my children are about to graduate, I'm finally a homeowner <strong>(Yay!)</strong>, 
        and ***** Eye Care has provided me the perfect environment and tools needed to become 
        an even better version of myself.
      </p>
      
      <div style="margin-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding-top: 15px; display: flex; gap: 15px;">
        <button style="background: none; border: 1px solid #a2c2e1; border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px 15px; color: #0056b3; cursor: pointer;">❤️ Like</button>
        <button style="background: none; border: 1px solid #a2c2e1; border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px 15px; color: #0056b3; cursor: pointer;">💭 Comment</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
